<div id="pf1" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="1"><div class="pc pc1 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="t m0 x1 h1 y1 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">克服神<span class="ff2">经网络的灾</span></div><div class="t m0 x2 h1 y2 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">难性遗忘问题</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf2" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="2"><div class="pc pc2 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="t m0 x3 h2 y3 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">迁移学<span class="ff2">习</span> 以及 <span class="ff2">继续学习</span> （<span class="ff3">continual</span> <span class="ff3">learning</span>）</span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y4 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">工<span class="ff5">业应用不常见一个模型解决多个问题</span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y5 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一个随<span class="ff5">时间改变了特征空间的分布的数据样本重新训练模型后变成了一个新</span></div><div class="t m1 x5 h5 y6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的模型</div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y7 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">即便是一个数据集，如果不小心<span class="ff5">选择</span></div><div class="t m0 x6 h6 y7 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">batch</div><div class="t m1 x7 h5 y7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x8 h6 y7 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">num</div><div class="t m1 x9 h4 y7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也会造成无法学<span class="ff5">习的情况</span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y8 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y8 ff7 fs3 fc0 sc1 ls0 ws0">但是真正的人工智能不是<span class="ff8 sc0">这样的，继续学习的问题必须解决</span></div><div class="t m0 x1 h7 y9 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _1"> </span><span class="fs5">the sequence of tasks may not be explicitly labelled, </span></div><div class="t m0 x1 h7 ya ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _1"> </span><span class="fs5">tasks may switch unpredictably, </span></div><div class="t m0 x1 h7 yb ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _1"> </span><span class="fs5">and any individual task may not recur for long time intervals</span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf3" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="3"><div class="pc pc3 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="t m0 x3 h8 yc ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">目前的<span class="ff3">workaround</span></div><div class="t m0 x3 h2 yd ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">一次<span class="ff2">训练全部的数据集（训练大量的数据集）</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 ye ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–<span class="_ _2"> </span><span class="ff6 fs2">Current approaches have typically ensured that data from all tasks are </span></div><div class="t m0 x5 h6 yf ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">simultaneously available during training</div><div class="t m0 x3 h2 y10 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">如果是<span class="ff2">时间序列的问题</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y11 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y11 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">使用<span class="ff5">强化学习玩</span></div><div class="t m0 xa h6 y11 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Atari</div><div class="t m1 xb h4 y11 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">游<span class="ff5">戏的，一种局面可能长时间不出现</span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y12 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y12 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">解决<span class="ff5">办法是添加</span> </div><div class="t m0 xc h6 y12 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">memory</div><div class="t m1 xd h5 y12 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> 和 </div><div class="t m0 xe h6 y12 ff6 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">replay</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf4" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="4"><div class="pc pc4 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="t m0 x3 h9 yc ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">仿生学<span class="ff2">带给我们希望</span> <span class="ff3">----</span> 插一条广告</div><div class="t m0 x3 ha y13 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一切没有仿生学依据的<span class="ff2">设计都是伪科学</span></div><div class="t m0 x3 h2 yd ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">人的神<span class="ff2">经网络里没有深度多层</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x3 h2 y14 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">人的神<span class="ff2">经网络里面没有<span class="ff3">BP</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x3 h2 y15 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff1 fs2">人学<span class="ff2">习一张动物图片不需要连续看上几十遍</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x3 hb y16 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="ff9 fs2 sc1">人在<span class="ffa sc0">连续学习的时候不需要同时将之前的任务完整的记忆下来</span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf5" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="5"><div class="pc pc5 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="data:image/png;base64,"/><div class="t m0 x3 h9 y17 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">哺乳<span class="ff2">动物如何学习</span></div><div class="t m0 x3 h3 y18 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _0"> </span><span class="fs2">Learning takes place through the formation and elimination of postsynaptic dendritic </span></div><div class="t m0 xf h6 y19 ff3 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spines over time</div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y1a ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y1a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学<span class="ff5">习是通过形成或者是消除<span class="ff8">突触后突状棘</span>发生的行为</span></div><div class="t m0 x4 h3 y1b ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">–</div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y1b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">一个跟之前学<span class="ff5">习到的任务相关的突出会受到某种保护，在学习新的任务的时</span></div><div class="t m1 x5 h4 y16 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">候收到的更改相<span class="ff5">对较少</span></div><div class="t m0 x1 hc y1c ff3 fs8 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws0">■<span class="_ _3"> </span><span class="fs9">----<span class="ff1"> </span>Sleep promotes branch-specific formation of dendritic spines after learning</span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
